============================================================================
This module was adopted by pscust@cpan.org
============================================================================

You can install this using in the usual Perl fashion

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install
        
The documentation is in the module file.  Once you install
the file, you can read it with perldoc.

	perldoc Text::MacroScript 
        
If you want to read it before you install it, you can use
perldoc directly on the module file.

	perldoc MacroScript.pm
        
This module repository is kept in Github, please feel free to submit issues, 
fork and send pull requests.

	https://github.com/pauloscustodio/Text-MacroScript


Enjoy, 

Paulo Custodio, pscust@cpan.org
